description: MSVChain is an intelligent, credible, open, decentralized credit data value platform built on the sharing economy. It is a low-level architecture based on the shared economy through blockchain technology. Through blockchain technology to subvert the existing centralized credit platform, MSV Chain aims to build value real and unique credit and credit system by using MSVChain token (“MSV”) to realize value quantification and value circulation within the platform. Sharing the economic credible ecosystem and truly realizing the great vision of “credit interconnection and sharing the future
